Perpetuity	#112.	 constantly &c. (very frequently). Phr. esto perpetuum [Lat.]
Permanence	#141.	 without a shadow of turning. Phr. esto perpetua [Lat.]
Veracity	#543.	 esto quod esse videris [Lat.]
Desire	#865.	 fain. Int. would that, would that it were!, O for!, esto perpetual [Lat.] the wish being father to the thought
Approbation	#931.	 may your shadow never be less!, esto perpetua! [Lat.], long life to!, viva!, enviva!, Godspeed!, valete et plaudite! [Lat.], encore!, bis!, probatum est [Lat.]
